 <head>
 </head>
 <body>
  <h1>
   <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/Drag_And_Drop/Reference/Time_Sources/Action_Icons/Reconfigure_Time_Source.png"/><br/>
   Reconfigure Time Source
  </h1>
  This action allows you to change the settings for an existing
  <span>
   Time Source
  </span>
  , specified in the "Time Source" field.
   
   
    The settings supplied here are the same as
  <a href="Create_Time_Source.htm">
   Create Time Source
  </a>
  , except for the parent.
   
   
    It will reset and deactivate the
  <span>
   Time Source
  </span>
  so you have to start it again.
  <h4>
   Action Syntax:
  </h4>
  <br/><img src="https://gms.magecorn.com/Manual/assets/Images/Scripting_Reference/Drag_And_Drop/Reference/Time_Sources/Action_Syntax/Reconfig_TS.png"/><br/>
  <h4>
   Arguments:
  </h4>
  <table>
   <tbody>
    <tr>
     <th>
      Argument
     </th>
     <th>
      Description
     </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Time Source
     </td>
     <td>
      The
      <span>
       <a href="../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Time_Sources/time_source_create.htm">
        Time Source ID
       </a>
      </span>
      to reconfigure
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Period
     </td>
     <td>
      The period length of the
      <span>
       Time Source
      </span>
      , how long it takes to expire
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Units
     </td>
     <td>
      The
      <a href="../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Time_Sources/Time_Source_Units.htm">
       units
      </a>
      that the period is expressed in (seconds or frames)
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Callback
     </td>
     <td>
      The
      <a href="../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Method_Variables.htm">
       method
      </a>
      to call when the
      <span>
       Time Source
      </span>
      expires
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Arguments
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       OPTIONAL
      </span>
      An
      <a href="../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Overview/Arrays.htm">
       array
      </a>
      containing the arguments to pass into the callback function
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Repetitions
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       OPTIONAL
      </span>
      How many times the
      <span>
       Time Source
      </span>
      should run in total, or -1 for indefinite repetition
     </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
     <td>
      Expiry Type
     </td>
     <td>
      <span>
       OPTIONAL
      </span>
      The
      <a href="../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Time_Sources/Time_Source_Expiry_Types.htm">
       expiry type
      </a>
      for the
      <span>
       Time Source
      </span>
     </td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
 </body>
</html>